      "description": "PFBC-linked PDGFB/PDGFRB and JAM2 defects impair pericyte-endothelial- astrocyte homeostasis, while related recessive pathways such as MYORG likely converge on the same neurovascular system. Reduced blood-brain barrier maintenance and cell-cell adhesion favor vascular and perivascular brain calcification.",
